transcript: I hate this apartment! I hate the color of these walls! I hate the fact that this place still smells like bird! I hate that singing guy!

transcript: Uh, I don't know, whatever.

transcript: I think it makes you look really dangerous.

transcript: Oh, I know. Y'know what, I never would've gotten this if it weren't for you. No really, when I'm with you I'm-I'm like this whole other guy, I love that guy! I mean, I love you too, a lot, but that guy! I-I love that guy!

transcript: I love both of you!

transcript: Yeah?

transcript: I wish I didn't have to go.

transcript: Ohh, Ross, please!

transcript: One more day, seriously/

speaker: ['Emily Waltham']
transcript: Don't do this to me, again. You'd know I'd stay here in a minute, but I'd really miss so much work, they'll fire me.
